0drones%20are%20exposing%20gaps%20in%20current%20air%20defense%20systems.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20cheap%20drones%20and%20massed%20missile%20attacks%20are%20testing%20the%20sophisticated%20air%20defense%20systems%20of%20the%20region's%20wealthiest%20powers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20sparked%20a%20race%20to%20deploy%20new%20experimental%20laser-based%20air%20defenses%20that%20military%20analysts%20say%20could%20help%20plug%20the%20gaps%20at%20a%20fraction%20of%20the%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIsrael%20is%20poised%20to%20become%20the%20first%20country%20in%20the%20region%20to%20deploy%20new%20laser%20air%20defenses.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FIsrael_MOD%2Fstatus%2F1850945386913157284%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%24500-million%20Iron%20Beam%3C%2Fa%3E%20won't%20replace%20Israel's%20Iron%20Dome%20missiles%20and%20other%20systems%2C%20but%20would%20complement%20them%20by%20adding%20a%20new%20layer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20laser%20system%20is%20the%20weapon%20of%20the%20future%2C%20capable%20of%20neutralizing%20an%20entire%20layer%20of%20threats%2C%26quot%3B%20Israel's%20defense%20minister%2C%20Israel%20Katz%2C%20said%20this%20month%20during%20a%20tour%20of%20facilities%20belonging%20to%20Rafael%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.timesofisrael.com%2Fliveblog_entry%2Fkatz-warns-israels-enemies-says-iron-beam-will-soon-be-ready%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20Israeli%20firm%20developing%20laser%20weapons.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hype%20around%20military%20lasers%20pre-dates%20the%20%26quot%3BStar%20Wars%26quot%3B%20movies%20and%20now%20centers%20on%20using%20these%20light%20weapons%20to%20zap%20drones%20and%20missiles%2C%20reducing%20the%20strain%20on%20guided%20missiles%20to%20do%20the%20same%20task.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20with%20no%20operational%20laser%20air%20defenses%2C%20it%20remains%20far%20from%20clear%20how%20these%20weapons%20will%20perform%20in%20various%20real-world%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227dfb119e-686e-4dd8-bbf6-725fc32d3a51%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECheap%20drone%20attacks%20expose%20gaps%20in%20defenses%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERecent%20conflicts%20have%20changed%20the%20dynamics%20of%20warfare%20in%20the%20Middle%20East.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIran-aligned%20groups%20such%20as%20the%20Houthi%20rebels%20in%20Yemen%20have%20deployed%20cheap%20drones%20to%20stress%20the%20US%20and%20Israel's%20missile-based%20air%20defense%20systems%2C%20using%20them%20to%20attack%20naval%20vessels%20and%20commercial%20ships%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHezbollah%20militia%20in%20Lebanon%20have%20also%20used%20drones%20to%20test%20Israel's%20Iron%20Dome%2C%20which%20was%20designed%20to%20shoot%20down%20ballistic%20missiles%20not%20low-flying%20UAVs%2C%20while%20Iran%20tried%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Firan-attack-israel-ballistic-missiles-overhyped-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoverwhelm%20the%20Iron%20Dome%20last%20year%20with%20barrages%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20drones%20and%20missiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20ease%20of%20acquiring%20commercial%20drone%20technologies%20and%20repurposing%20them%20for%20military%20use%20has%20enabled%20both%20state%20and%20non-state%20actors%20to%20field%20such%20offensive%20systems%20in%20increasing%20numbers%2C%26quot%3B%20James%20Black%2C%20assistant%20director%20at%20RAND%20Europe%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20laser%20defenses%20offer%20a%20potentially%20cheap%20and%20accurate%20system%20for%20defending%20against%20new%20threats%20from%20the%20air.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20drones%20cost%20as%20little%20as%20%242%2C000%2C%20missiles%20used%20to%20take%20them%20down%20can%20cost%20around%20%242%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20layer%20of%20laser%20defenses%20could%20help%20with%20the%20costs%20and%20give%20the%20missiles-based%20systems%20time%20to%20reload%20or%20plug%20gaps%20where%20other%20systems%20are%20vulnerable%2C%26quot%3B%20Sascha%20Bruchmann%2C%20a%20research%20fellow%20at%20the%20International%20Institute%20for%20Strategic%20Studies%20in%20Bahrain%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20difficulty%20of%20stopping%20drones%20has%20an%20added%20challenge%2C%20two%20retired%20Israeli%20generals%20previously%20warned%3A%20Air%20defenses%20need%20more%20ways%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisrael-air-defense-system-vulnerable-drones-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edefeat%20drones%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20risk%20being%20knocked%20out%20of%20action%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226a95a29d-d8e4-4c64-9f58-fcc40c8c9a02%5C%22%3EThe%20race%20for%20laser%20weapons%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.defensenews.com%2Fglobal%2Fmideast-africa%2F2025%2F02%2F14%2Fas-israel-fields-iron-beam-gulf-states-are-pining-for-the-technology%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDefense%20News%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Rafael%2C%20the%20Israeli%20defense%20firm%2C%20had%20displayed%20its%20laser%20air%20defense%20technology%20at%20weapons%20shows%20in%20Abu%20Dhabi%2C%20indicating%20it%20may%20be%20prepared%20to%20sell%20the%20tech%20to%20other%20regional%20powers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERafael%20didn't%20respond%20to%20a%20Business%20Insider%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESaudi%20Arabia%20is%20also%20developing%20its%20own%20laser%20air%20defense%20capacity%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.defensemirror.com%2Fnews%2F32959%2FSaudi_Arabia_Deploys_China_made_Laser_firing_Anti_drone_System_against_Houthi_UAVs%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20using%20Chinese%20systems%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20according%20to%20reports%2C%20while%20the%20UAE%20is%20seeking%20to%20develop%20its%20own%20laser%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELasers%20are%20designed%20to%20direct%20an%20intense%20beam%20of%20light%20that%20uses%20heat%20to%20cut%20through%20a%20target.%20They%20can%20engage%20%26quot%3Bmultiple%20targets%20at%20a%20low%20cost%20per%20shot%2C%26quot%3B%20Black%20said%2C%20adding%20they%20do%20this%20%26quot%3Bwithout%20the%20risk%20of%20running%20out%20of%20missiles%20or%20ammunition%20in%20the%20way%20that%20traditional%20air%20defense%20systems%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20UK%20Ministry%20of%20Defence%20has%20said%20that%20costs%20could%20be%20as%20low%20as%20tens%20of%20dollars%20per%20shot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20a%20laser%20must%20have%20impressive%20accuracy%20to%20stay%20on%20a%20point%20long%20enough%20to%20burn%20through%20it%20%E2%80%94%20no%20easy%20feat%20against%20a%20ballistic%20missile%20traveling%20over%20five%20times%20the%20speed%20of%20sound.%20Or%20it%20must%20have%20sufficient%20power%20to%20rapidly%20burn%20through%20a%20target.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20added%20challenge%20is%20that%20missiles%20could%20be%20adapted%20with%20plastics%20and%20metals%20that%20are%20more%20resistant%20to%20lasers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22692c8d58-8533-4218-a7d1-93b58ad90e20%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ENot%20a%20silver%20bullet%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELasers%20may%20prove%20to%20be%20better%20drone%20killers%20than%20missile%20interceptors.%20But%20laser%20weapons%20are%20yet%20to%20be%20deployed%20at%20scale%2C%20and%20remain%20experimental.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBad%20weather%20or%20smoke%20can%20also%20interfere%20with%20the%20strength%20and%20precision%20of%20a%20beam%2C%20and%20generating%20the%20power%20needed%20in%20remote%20front-line%20regions%20remains%20a%20challenge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBlack%20said%20weapons%20systems%20take%20time%20and%20money%20to%20refine%2C%20with%20Rafael's%20laser%20air%20defense%20systems%20in%20development%20for%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMultiple%20breakthroughs%20were%20necessary%20along%20the%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20which%20%26quot%3Bpriced%20out%20many%20nations%2C%20as%20others%20grew%20disillusioned%20and%20cynical.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYuval%20Steinitz%2C%20Rafael's%20chairman%2C%20said%20at%20a%20media%20briefing%20in%20December%20that%20one%20challenge%20they%20faced%20was%20that%20with%20larger%20lasers%2C%20the%20air%20density%20in%20the%20atmosphere%20disperses%20the%20power%20of%20the%20beam.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20had%20to%20find%20a%20way%20to%20bypass%20the%20atmosphere%20and%20keep%20the%20lasers%20as%20strong%20as%20when%20they%20were%26quot%3B%20fired%2C%20he%20said%2C%20explaining%20that%20they%20resolved%20this%20by%20shooting%20smaller%20beams%20that%20then%20converge%20on%20vulnerable%20points%20on%20a%20target%20to%20disable%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20clashes%20between%20countries%20like%20Israel%20and%20Iran%20%E2%80%94%20and%20in%20defending%20oil%20and%20gas%20infrastructure%20in%20places%20like%20Saudi%20Arabia%20%E2%80%94%20laser%20weapons%20might%20not%20be%20an%20instant%20fix%2C%20but%20they're%20moving%20closer%20to%20a%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20whole%20series%20of%20technologies%20that%20is%20just%20becoming%20small%2C%20light%2C%20precise%2C%20and%20rugged%20enough%20to%20allow%20a%20military%20application%2C%26quot%3B%20Bruchmann%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Brather%20than%20an%20experimental%20one%20that%20always%20seemed%20so%20close%20to%20a%20working%20weapon.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-allies-israel-middle-east-racing-develop-laser-defense-weapons-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742899605000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d9586469253ccddf9986d4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-allies-israel-middle-east-racing-develop-laser-defense-weapons-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Cheap%20drones%20are%20exposing%20gaps%20in%20current%20air%20defense%20systems%2C%20and%20countries%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20are%20looking%20to%20laser%20weapons%20for%20answers.%