ion%20on%20the%20parade%20ground%20and%20showcased%20its%20might%20on%20the%20occasion%20of%20Pakistan%20Day%20two%20days%20ago%20(March%2023)%2C%20facts%20indicate%20that%20it%20is%20riven%20with%20divisions%20on%20an%20unprecedented%20scale.%20Apart%20from%20near-daily%20attacks%20on%20itself%2C%20the%20army%20has%20turned%20into%20a%20brute%20force%2C%20with%20its%20%E2%80%98counter-terrorism'%20operations%20not%20differentiating%20even%20children%20or%20women%20from%20terrorists.%20That's%20terrible%20for%20the%20people%20on%20the%20receiving%20end%2C%20but%20deeply%20corrosive%20also%20for%20the%20forces%20that%20undertake%20such%20actions.%20So%20what%20explains%20the%20rumours%20of%20deep%20resentment%20within%20the%20lower%20ranks%2C%20and%2C%20if%20reports%20are%20to%20be%20believed%2C%20calls%20for%20the%20Army%20Chief%20to%20resign%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Bloody%20War%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20parade%20itself%20was%20held%20with%20all%20fanfare%2C%20with%20a%20rather%20uncomfortable%20looking%20Prime%20Minister%20in%20front%2C%20while%20President%20Zardari%20delivered%20the%20formal%20address.%20Behind%20him%20was%20the%20Army%20Chief%20and%20his%20cohorts.%20The%20whole%20seating%20arrangement%20could%20have%20been%20reversed%20and%20nobody%20would%20have%20batted%20an%20eye%2C%20so%20obviously%20was%20the%20Army%20Chief%20in%20charge.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20recent%20attacks%20on%20his%20forces%E2%80%94not%20just%20the%20hijack%20of%20the%20Jaffar%20express%20but%20also%20a%20series%20of%20attacks%20thereafter%20not%20just%20in%20Balochistan%2C%20but%20also%20in%20the%20highly%20unstable%20Khyber%20Pakhtunkhwa%20region%E2%80%94have%20called%20into%20question%20the%20Army's%20slipping%20grip.%20Reports%20from%20Pakistani%20think-tanks%20have%20already%20highlighted%202024%20as%20the%20worst%20year%20on%20record%20in%20a%20decade%20in%20terms%20of%20terror%20attacks%3B%20the%20graph%20is%20likely%20to%20only%20rise%20this%20year.%20Reports%20indicate%20that%20there%20have%20been%20179%20incidents%20till%20March%2011%20with%20255%20casualties%2C%20which%20include%20members%20of%20the%20Army%2C%20Frontier%20Corps%2C%20Levies%2C%20Constabulary%2C%20the%20Inter-Services%20Intelligence%20(ISI)%2C%20and%20Police.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20rage%2C%20the%20Pakistan%20army%20acted%20exactly%20as%20per%20precedent.%20It%20turned%20upon%20the%20hapless%20population%2C%20firing%20on%20crowds%2C%20including%20children%2C%20and%20picking%20up%20those%20who%20have%20stood%20up%20peacefully%20for%20Baloch%20rights.%20That%20includes%20the%20charismatic%20Mehrang%20Baloch%2C%20who%20is%20fast%20being%20made%20into%20a%20leader%20of%20repute%2C%20ironically%20due%20to%20the%20actions%20of%20the%20army%20itself.%20She%20has%20been%20charged%20with%20sedition%20and%20terrorism%2C%20all%20for%20staging%20a%20sit-in%20at%20a%20university.%20But%20anger%20within%20Balochistan%20is%20growing.%20Quetta%20erupted%20with%20protests%20after%20her%20arrest%20and%20hundreds%20turned%20up%20for%20the%20funerals%20of%20those%20killed.%20As%20the%20numbers%20mount%2C%20so%20will%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20Counter-Strategy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmazingly%2C%20the%20Pakistan%20army%2C%20arguably%20the%20most%20experienced%20%E2%80%98terrorist'-sponsoring%20army%20in%20the%20world%2C%20seems%20to%20have%20no%20conception%20at%20all%20about%20counter-terrorism%20in%20its%20own%20country.%20It%20has%20bombed%2C%20strafed%20and%20used%20artillery%20against%20its%20own%20citizens%2C%20even%20taking%20journalists%20on%20an%20air%20ride%20to%20see%20the%20destruction%20caused%20in%20Khyber%20Pakhtunkhwa%2C%20where%20hundreds%20upon%20hundreds%20of%20houses%20had%20roofs%20missing%20even%20as%20some%2072%2C000%20fled%20the%20area.%20That%20was%202016.%20Anyone%20with%20a%20modicum%20of%20knowledge%20would%20have%20said%20that%20things%20were%20likely%20to%20get%20much%20worse%20roughly%20three%20to%20four%20years%20down%20the%20line.%20That's%20how%20much%20it%20takes%20for%20an%20angry%20population%20to%20turn%20upon%20its%20tormentors%2C%20and%20for%20resistance%20groups%20to%20regroup.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20that%20did%20happen.%20Now%2C%20there%20are%20few%20areas%20where%20Pakistani%20forces%20can%20move%20with%20impunity.%20That%20also%20applies%20to%20Balochistan%2C%20which%20has%20been%20treated%20with%20colonial%20contempt.%20But%20the%20real%20downside%20is%20this%3A%20such%20operations%20against%20one's%20own%20people%20have%20eroded%20the%20cohesion%20of%20the%20army%20that%20is%20fighting%20it.%20Armies%20are%20honed%20and%20trained%20on%20%E2%80%98honour'%20in%20battle%20against%20an%20%E2%80%98enemy'%2C%20for%20which%20valour%20they%20are%20rewarded%20and%20respected%2C%20most%20of%20all%20from%20the%20villages%20they%20come%20from.%20But%20fighting%20civilians%20and%20children%20carry%20no%20such%20benefits%2C%20and%20no%20army%20man%2C%20whether%20Pakistani%20or%20Indian%2C%20will%20tolerate%20this.%20That%20is%20the%20core%20reason%20why%20the%20Indian%20army%20has%20had%20the%20sense%20to%20fight%20with%20%E2%80%98one%20hand%20behind%20its%20back'%2C%20and%20why%20it%20organised%20its%20own%20outreach%20programmes%20such%20as%20%E2%80%98Sadhbhavana'%2C%20which%20has%20a%20range%20of%20initiatives%20aimed%20at%20providing%20services%20to%20populations%20in%20insurgency-hit%20areas.%20That's%20not%20just%20morality%2C%20it's%20an%20operational%20necessity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMissing%20In%20Action%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%20army's%20governance%20is%20%E2%80%9Cmissing%20in%20action%E2%80%9D.%20Recent%20reports%20indicate%20that%20even%20a%20star%20project%20such%20as%20the%20Gwadar%20deep%20sea%20port%20has%20remained%20in%20limbo%20due%20to%20the%20unavailability%20of%20even%20basic%20drinking%20water%20and%20a%20power%20source.%20Not%20that%20China%20hasn't%20supplied%20the%20required%20equipment.%20The%20recent%20meeting%20by%20Ahsan%20Iqbal%2C%20Federal%20Minister%20for%20Planning%20was%20told%20that%2010%2C000%20Chinese%20solar%20panels%20were%20delivered%20in%20May%202024%2C%20followed%20by%20another%205%2C000%20in%20September%2C%20under%20a%20grant-in-aid%20programme%2C%20apart%20from%20much%20else.%20China%20rather%20sensibly%20had%20also%20provided%20grants%20for%20a%20desalination%20plant%20and%20a%20huge%20hospital%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20woo%20the%20Baloch.%20None%20of%20that%20is%20operational.%20Despite%20providing%20Pakistan%20with%20natural%20gas%20to%20sustain%20its%20economy%2C%20the%20state%20itself%20faces%20a%20severe%20lack%20of%20power.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20point%20here%20is%20that%20it's%20the%20Pakistan%20army%20that's%20in%20the%20driving%20seat%20in%20the%20Balochistan%20province.%20Nothing%20moves%E2%80%94quite%20literally%E2%80%94without%20the%20say-so%20of%20the%20security%20forces%2C%20in%20this%20case%2C%20the%20X11%20Corps%20with%20its%20two%20Infantry%20Divisions%2C%20as%20well%20as%20an%20unknown%20number%20of%20Pakistani%20Rangers%2C%20a%20paramilitary%20force%20that%20comes%20under%20the%20direct%20command%20of%20the%20army%20in%20crisis%20situations.%20Then%20are%20several%20thousands%20of%20troops%20of%20the%20Frontier%20Corps%2C%20which%20have%20only%20increased%20in%20strength%20in%20recent%20months.%20Even%20with%20all%20this%2C%20Balochistan%2C%20as%20lawmakers%20say%2C%20is%20out%20of%20the%20control%20of%20the%20state.%20It%20was%20not%20just%20Maulana%20Fazlur%20Rehman%20who%20said%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20the%20house%20that%20%E2%80%9CPakistan's%20physical%20boundaries%20might%20be%20altered%20sooner%20rather%20than%20later%E2%80%9D.%20The%20opinion%20was%20also%20echoed%20by%20former%20Interior%20Minister%20Rana%20Sanaullah%2C%20a%20trusted%20advisor%20of%20the%20government.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20the%20Pakistan%20army%2C%20which%20not%20only%20runs%20counter-terrorism%20operations%20but%20also%20heads%20almost%20everything%20in%20the%20state%2C%20including%20the%20Strategic%20Investment%20Facilitation%20Council%2C%20the%20lead%20body%20intended%20to%20%E2%80%98drive'%20investment%20into%20a%20declining%20state%2C%20not%20to%20mention%20a%20%24100-billion%20economic%20empire%2C%20seems%20to%20have%20failed%20at%20all%20its%20tasks.%20Rampant%20insurgency%2C%20a%20declining%20economy%20and%2C%20if%20reports%20are%20to%20be%20believed%2C%20a%20large%20group%20of%20junior%20officers%20shooting%20off%20a%20letter%20demanding%20that%20the%20Army%20Chief%20resign%2C%20are%20testament%20to%20the%20Pakistan%20Army's%20failures.%20The%20%E2%80%98secret'%20letter%2C%20by%20the%20way%2C%20accuses%20the%20Army%20Chief%20of%20dragging%20the%20institution%20into%20muck%20and%20using%20it%20for%20his%20own%20vendetta.%20This%20is%20powerful%20stuff.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EGlory%20Days%2C%20Gone%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20an%20army%20that%20once%20used%20to%20get%20praise%20for%20its%20professionalism%2C%20earning%20at%20times%20the%20envy%20of%20its%20%E2%80%98enemy'%20for%20its%20absolute%20discipline%20and%20superior%20position%20in%20society.%20That%20is%20all%20history.%20Today%2C%20the%20army%20is%20seen%20as%20an%20oppressor%20and%20a%20bandit%20force%20(remember%20that%20the%20ISI%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20extorting%20money%20from%20businessmen).%20Most%20vitally%2C%20its%20extreme%20violence%20has%20caught%20the%20attention%20of%20the%20world.%20As%20of%20today%2C%20all%20major%20newspapers%2C%20including%20the%20%3Cem%3ENew%20York%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20are%20covering%20the%20%E2%80%98forgotten%20war'%20that%20has%20been%20Balochistan%20in%20the%20last%20four%20decades.%20Mehran%20Baloch%20is%20nominated%20for%20the%20Nobel%2C%20while%20her%20compatriots%20are%20slated%20for%20the%20prestigious%20Nelson%20Mandela%20Prize.%20The%20world%20is%20sitting%20up%20to%20take%20notice%2C%20and%20not%20in%20a%20good%20way.%20The%20irony%3A%20none%20other%20than%20the%20Pakistan%20army%2C%20or%20rather%2C%20its%20leadership%2C%20has%20made%20this%20happen%20over%20the%20years.%20It%20may%20well%20be%20payback%20time%20now.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Tara%20Kartha%20is%20a%20former%20director%20of%20the%20National%20Security%20Council%20Secretariat)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742898180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F36gor8fc_pakistan-army_625x300_09_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fis-it-payback-time-for-pakistan-army-8006830%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Reports%20from%20Pakistani%20think-tanks%20have%20already%20highlighted%202024%20as%20the%20worst%20year%20on%20record%20in%20a%20decade%20in%20terms%20of%20terror%20attacks%3B%20the%20graph%20is%20likely%20to%20only%20rise%20this%20year.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20eyes%20tariff%20cuts%20on%20over%20half%20of%20US%20imports%20worth%20%2423%20bn%2C%20says%20report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742897978000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-119473909%2Cimgsize-43548.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Findia-us-trade-deal-modi-government-eyes-tariff-cuts-on-more-than-half-of-us-imports-worth-23-billion-says-report%2Farticleshow%2F119473879.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20plans%20to%20reduce%20tariffs%20on%20over%2050%25%20of%20US%20imports%20worth%20%2423%20billion%20under%20a%20new%20trade%20agreement%20to%20prevent%20reciprocal%20tariffs.%20Negotiations%20are%20set%20to%20address%20these%20changes%2C%20with%20India%20pursuing%20balanced%20reforms%