ward%2050.%20One%20(former)%20friend%20suggested%20I%20was%20being%20selfish%2C%20as%20I'd%20likely%20end%20up%20being%20a%20financial%20or%20emotional%20burden%20on%20my%20daughter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20be%20lying%20if%20I%20said%20I%20hadn't%20had%20several%20sleepless%20nights%20batting%20away%20imagined%20realities%20of%20myself%20as%20a%20wizened%20older%20parent%2C%20an%20embarrassment%20and%20health%20hindrance%20to%20a%2020-something%20daughter.%20But%20that%20fear%20pushed%20me%20to%20prioritize%20my%20health%20with%20good%20lifestyle%20habits%2C%20regular%20exercise%2C%20and%20routine%20check-ups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20it%20hasn't%20stopped%20me%20from%20occasionally%20being%20mistaken%20for%20my%20child's%20grandmother%20(something%20my%20daughter%20finds%20hilarious)%20%E2%80%94%20but%20I'm%20still%20fitter%20than%20I%20ever%20was%20in%20my%20partying%2020s%20and%2030s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhabits-that-age-you-faster-make-you-look-older-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworry%20about%20aging%3C%2Fa%3E.%20My%2080-year-old%20mom%20is%20thriving%20and%20there%20for%20me%20when%20I%20need%20her%3B%20my%20daughter%20might%20not%20have%20that%20same%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20broader%20level%2C%20I%20also%20fret%20about%20the%20uncertain%20future%20that%20awaits%20her.%20With%20the%20climate%20crisis%2C%20the%20rise%20of%20AI%20and%20automated%20jobs%2C%20and%20skyrocketing%20property%20costs%2C%20I%20worry%20about%20whether%20she%20will%20be%20OK%20if%20I'm%20not%20around%20to%20help%20her%20handle%20these%20challenges%2C%20as%20so%20many%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-living-at-home-relying-on-parents-safety-net-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20parents%20of%20Gen%20Z%20adults%3C%2Fa%3E%20currently%20are.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20despite%20those%20anxieties%2C%20I%20know%20I'm%20better%20off%20as%20an%20olde