20anti-personnel%20mines.%3Cp%3EJake%20Epstein%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ERussia's%20invasion%20has%20turned%20Ukraine%20into%20the%20most%20heavily%20mined%20country%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EUkraine's%20deminers%20are%20tasked%20with%20cleaning%20up%20the%20deadly%20mess%2C%20which%20will%20take%20years.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETo%20help%20them%20do%20this%20safely%2C%20deminers%20use%20a%20small%20robot%20and%20other%20tools.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EBILA%20TSERKVA%2C%20Ukraine%20%E2%80%94%20For%20the%20demining%20crews%20of%20Ukraine's%20State%20Emergency%20Services%2C%20removing%20Russian%20explosives%20is%20a%20dangerous%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20individuals%20are%20tasked%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-war-russia-land-mines-cleanup-booby-traps-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecleaning%20up%20land%20mines%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20fallen%20missiles%2C%20and%20other%20unexploded%20ordnance%20from%20fields%20and%20villages%20across%20the%20Ukrainian%20countryside.%20Their%20work%20must%20be%20done%20cautiously%2C%20as%20one%20wrong%20move%20could%20prove%20fatal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20even%20when%20the%20Russian%20bombs%20stop%20falling%20one%20day%2C%20the%20work%20will%20continue%20for%20years%20to%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine%20is%20now%20the%20most%20heavily%20mined%20country%20in%20the%20world%2C%20with%20up%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.undp.org%2Feuropean-union%2Fstories%2Fukraine-tackling-mine-action-all-sides-make-land-safe-again%23%3A~%3Atext%3DUkraine%2520is%2520now%2520the%2520most%2520mined%2520country%2Cof%2520contamination%2520with%2520landmines%2520and%2520unexploded%2520ordnance.%26amp%3Btext%3DUNDP%2520Ukraine%2520is%2520leading%2520a%2520comprehensive%25205%252Dyear%2Cexplosive%2520devices%2520and%2520explosive%2520remnants%2520of%2520war.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E23%25%20of%20its%20territory%3C%2Fa%3E%20potentially%20contaminated%20with%20land%20mines%20and%20unexploded%20ordnance%2C%20according%20to%20the%20United%20Nations%20Development%20Programme.%20Some%20other%20estimates%20say%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcepa.org%2Farticle%2Fan-explosive-choice-landmines-and-ukraine%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethis%20figure%20is%20even%20higher%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20clearing%20such%20a%20mess%20will%20cost%20tens%20of%20billions%20of%20dollars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20help%20clean%20up%20land%20mines%20and%20minimize%20the%20risk%20to%20humans%2C%20the%20State%20Emergency%20Service%20relies%20on%20a%20collection%20of%20drones%20and%20robots%20to%20spot%20and%20then%20remove%20the%20buried%20explosives.%20Business%20Insider%20recently%20met%20with%20two%20members%20of%20a%2072-person%20demining%20unit%20that%20operates%20these%20tools%20to%20see%20how%20they%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20mine-clearing%20site%20south%20of%20Kyiv%2C%20the%20deminers%20explained%20to%20BI%20how%20they%20remove%20mines%20from%20the%20ground.%20One%20of%20the%20safest%20ways%20they%20do%20this%20is%20with%20the%20help%20of%20a%20small%2C%20remote-controlled%20robot%20resembling%20the%20character%20%26quot%3BWALL-E%26quot%3B%20from%20the%20animated%20film%20of%20the%20same%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20fully%20compact%20demining%20robot.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67e1ca6563d72727e1981e6b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20fully%20compact%20demining%20robot.%3Cp%3EJake%20Epstein%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20demining%20robot%20can%20extend%20its%20arm%20to%20remove%20mines%20from%20the%20ground.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67e1cac663d72727e1981e80%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3