20in%20London%2C%20Saurabh%20was%20visiting%20Meerut%20for%20his%20daughter's%20birthday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Saurabh%20Wanted%20To%20Take%20Daughter%20To%20London'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20police%20sources%2C%20the%20investigation%20has%20revealed%20that%20Saurabh's%20London%20visa%20was%20about%20to%20expire%20and%20he%20had%20planned%20to%20renew%20it%20during%20this%20visit%20home.%20Saurabh%20also%20wanted%20to%20take%20his%20wife%20and%20daughter%20to%20London%20with%20him.%20But%20Muskaan%20had%20rejected%20this%20plan%20and%20said%20she%20wanted%20to%20stay%20in%20Meerut%2C%20presumably%20to%20be%20with%20Sahil.%20Saurabh%20had%20then%20decided%20that%20he%20would%20take%20his%20daughter%20along%20and%20had%20also%20applied%20for%20a%20passport%20for%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Night%20Of%20Murder%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20probe%20so%20far%2C%20Muskaan%20drugged%20Saurabh%20with%20sleeping%20pills%20on%20the%20night%20of%20March%203.%20Once%20he%20dozed%20off%2C%20she%20stabbed%20him%20thrice%20with%20a%20knife.%20She%20then%20used%20the%20cut-throat%20razor%20to%20slit%20his%20throat.%20The%20task%20of%20severing%20the%20head%20from%20the%20torso%20fell%20to%20Sahil%2C%20who%20used%20a%20knife%20for%20this%2C%20the%20probe%20has%20found.%20The%20two%20then%20chopped%20off%20the%20body%20into%2015%20pieces.%20These%20pieces%20were%20thrown%20into%20the%20drum%20and%20sealed%20with%20wet%20cement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPlant%20Plan%20Out%2C%20Cement%20Plan%20In%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20investigation%20and%20the%20accused's%20statements%2C%20the%20initial%20plan%20was%20to%20pour%20mud%20over%20Saurabh's%20body%20parts%20and%20plant%20a%20sapling%20in%20the%20drum.%20But%20later%2C%20Muskaan%20and%20Sahil%20considered%20the%20stench%20factor%20and%20decided%20that%20wet%20cement%20would%20be%20a%20better%20option%20to%20conceal%20