0owe%20ourselves%20dialogue%2C%20dissent%2C%20and%20dignity%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Mehta%20posted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20September%202020%2C%20a%20part%20of%20Kangana%20Ranaut's%20Mumbai%20office%20was%20demolished%20by%20the%20Brihanmumbai%20Municipal%20Corporation%2C%20citing%20encroachment.%20The%20timing%20of%20the%20action%20raised%20questions.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20the%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20government%20was%20in%20power%20in%20Maharashtra%20and%20also%20controlled%20the%20civic%20body.%20The%20action%20against%20Kangana%20followed%20a%20bitter%20spat%20between%20her%20and%20Shiv%20Sena%20leaders%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20actor%20Sushant%20Singh%20Rajput's%20shocking%20death.%C2%A0The%20actor%20moved%20court%20against%20the%20demolition%20and%20scored%20a%20big%20win%20there.%20The%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20paused%20the%20demolition%20exercise%20and%20questioned%20the%20motives%20behind%20the%20BMC's%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20today%2C%20Ms%20Ranaut%20slammed%20Kunal%20Kamra's%20jokes%20targeting%20Mr%20Shinde%20and%20said%20it%20was%20not%20okay%20to%20disrespect%20someone%20for%20his%20humble%20background.%20The%20actor%20said%20the%202020%20move%20against%20her%20was%20%26quot%3Billegal%26quot%3B%2C%20but%20the%20action%20against%20the%20comic%20now%20is%20%26quot%3Blegal%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742894700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fb6haj548_hansal-mehta-kangana_625x300_25_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkunal-kamra-row-filmmaker-hansal-mehta-vs-kangana-ranaut-over-kunal-kamra-row-8006135%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Filmmaker%20Hansal%20Mehta%20and%20actor-MP%20Kangana%20Ranaut%20clashed%20online%20today%20over%20the%20crackdown%20against%20stand-up%20comic%20Kunal%20Kamra%20for%20his%20jokes%20targeting%20Shiv%20Sena%20chief%20Eknath%20Shinde.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%