0Vance%20expressed%20doubts%20about%20carrying%20out%20the%20strikes%2C%20saying%20he%20hated%20%26quot%3Bbailing%20Europe%20out%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20countries%20there%20were%20more%20affected%20by%20Houthi%20attacks%20on%20shipping%20than%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoldberg%20wrote%20that%20Hegseth%20sent%20information%20on%20the%20strikes%2C%20including%20%26quot%3Btargets%2C%20weapons%20the%20US%20would%20be%20deploying%2C%20and%20attack%20sequencing%2C%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20group%20chat%C2%A0at%2011%3A44%20a.m%2C%20around%20two%20hours%20before%20the%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAccording%20to%20the%20lengthy%20Hegseth%20text%2C%20the%20first%20detonations%20in%20Yemen%20would%20be%20felt%20two%20hours%20hence%2C%20at%201%3A45%20pm%20Eastern%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Goldberg%20wrote%20--%20a%20timeline%20that%20was%20borne%20out%20on%20the%20ground%20in%20Yemen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGroup%20chat%20contributors%20identified%20as%20National%20Security%20Advisor%20Mike%20Waltz%20and%20Hegseth%20both%20sent%20messages%20arguing%20only%20Washington%20had%20the%20capability%20to%20carry%20out%20the%20strikes%2C%20with%20the%20latter%20official%20saying%20he%20shared%20Vance's%20%26quot%3Bloathing%20of%20European%20free-loading.%20It's%20PATHETIC.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20a%20person%20identified%20as%20%26quot%3BS%20M%26quot%3B%20--%20possibly%20Trump%20advisor%20Stephen%20Miller%20--%20argued%20that%20%26quot%3Bif%20the%20US%20successfully%20restores%20freedom%20of%20navigation%20at%20great%20cost%20there%20needs%20to%20be%20some%20further%20economic%20gain%20extracted%20in%20return.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20leak%20could%20have%20been%20highly%20damaging%20if%20Goldberg%20had%20publicized%20details%20of%20the%20plan%20in%20advance%2C%20but%20he%20did%20not%20do%20so%20even%20after%20the%20fact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EPete%20Hegseth%20Slams%20Goldberg%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20he%20spoke%20to%20reporters%20Monday%20Hegseth%20dodged%20questions%20about%20the%20leak%2C%20in%20which%20highly%20sensitive%20material%20was%20not%20only%20shared%20with%20a%20reporter%20but%20also%20on%20a%20commercial%20app%20rather%20than%20in%20secure%20military%20channels%20reserved%20for%20such%20communications.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20Fox%20News%20host%20with%20no%20experience%20running%20a%20huge%20organization%20like%20the%20Pentagon%2C%20took%20no%20responsibility%20for%20the%20security%20breach%20as%20he%20spoke%20to%20reporters%20late%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20instead%20attacked%20Goldberg%20and%20insisted%20that%20%26quot%3Bnobody%20was%20texting%20war%20plans%2C%26quot%3B%20despite%20the%20White%20House%20confirming%20the%20breach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20White%20House%20said%20President%20Trump%20%26quot%3Bcontinues%20to%20have%20the%20utmost%20confidence%20in%20his%20national%20security%20team%2C%26quot%3B%20after%20the%20US%20president%20earlier%20said%20he%20did%20not%20%26quot%3Bknow%20anything%20about%26quot%3B%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHouthi%20Attacks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Houthi%20rebels%2C%20who%20have%20controlled%20much%20of%20Yemen%20for%20more%20than%20a%20decade%2C%20are%20part%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Baxis%20of%20resistance%26quot%3B%20of%20pro-Iran%20groups%20staunchly%20opposed%20to%20Israel%20and%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20have%20launched%20scores%20of%20drone%20and%20missile%20attacks%20at%20ships%20passing%20Yemen%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%20and%20Gulf%20of%20Aden%20during%20the%20Gaza%20war%2C%20saying%20they%20were%20carried%20out%20in%20solidarity%20with%20Palestinians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Houthis'%20campaign%20crippled%20the%20vital%20route%2C%20which%20normally%20carries%20about%2012%20per%20cent%20of%20world%20shipping%20traffic%2C%20forcing%20many%20companies%20into%20a%20costly%20detour%20around%20the%20tip%20of%20southern%20Africa