20kg%20wooden%20cross%20as%20a%20plea%20for%20former%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Chief%20Minister%20J%20Jayalalithaa's%20return%20to%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202005%2C%20he%20had%20painted%2056%20portraits%20of%20Ms%20Jayalalithaa%20using%20his%20own%20blood%20for%20her%2056th%20birthday.%20In%202013%2C%20he%20created%20a%20frozen%20blood%20bust%20of%20the%20leader%20using%2011%20liters%20of%20blood%2C%20including%20his%20own.%20These%20acts%20were%20even%20condemned%20by%20Ms%20Jayalalithaa%20who%20had%20advised%20him%20to%20refrain%20from%20performing%20them.%20Later%20on%2C%20he%20had%20unveiled%20a%2022-foot%20bronze%20statue%20of%20Pope%20John%20Paul%20II%2C%20sculpting%20statues%20of%20Indian-origin%20astronaut%20Kalpana%20Chawla%2C%20and%20painting%20former%20Sri%20Lankan%20President%20Mahinda%20Rajapaksa's%20portrait%20using%20pig's%20blood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20sensational%20act%20was%20when%20Mr%20Hussaini%20allowed%20101%20cars%20to%20be%20driven%20on%20his%20right%20hand%20and%20broke%205%2C000%20tiles%20and%201%2C000%20bricks%20in%20succession.%20He%20also%20survived%20being%20bitten%20by%20a%20venomous%20cobra.%20Mr%20Hussaini%20had%20also%20once%20set%20himself%20on%20fire%20with%20140%20liters%20of%20petrol.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%201980s%2C%20Mr%20Hussaini%20was%20falsely%20accused%20of%20being%20a%20Sri%20Lankan%20terrorist%20and%20was%20jailed%20for%2010%20days%20at%20Tihar%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Hussaini%20made%20his%20acting%20debut%20in%201986%20with%20actor%20Kamal%20Haasan's%20movie%20'Punnagai%20Mannan'.%20He%20became%20a%20part%20of%20many%20movies%20such%20as%20Bloodstone%2C%20Unnai%20Solli%20Kutramillai%2C%20Badri%2C%20Kaathuvaakula%20Rendu%20Kaadhal%2C%20Chennai%20City%20Gangsters%2C%20and%20Vedan.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742893620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Ffar1252o_hussaini_625x300_25_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fshiha