0past%20year%20and%20rang%20even%20more%20in%20the%20past%20few%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20last%20six%20months%20have%20been%20pretty%20crazy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BEvery%20reputable%20family%20office%20and%20institution%20wants%20to%20know%2C%20how%20can%20I%20buy%20this%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMoses%20was%20one%20of%20five%20VCs%2C%20and%20brokers%20BI%20spoke%20with%20who%20described%20intense%20demand%20but%20limited%20supply%20for%20secondary%20shares%20of%20Anduril%2C%20the%20defense%20tech%20startup%20founded%20in%202017%20by%20Palmer%20Luckey%2C%20a%2032-year-old%20entrepreneur%20with%20a%20penchant%20for%20mullets%20and%20colorful%20Hawaiian%20shirts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20stock%20in%20public%20companies%20like%20Amazon%20or%20Google%2C%20which%20anyone%20can%20instantly%20buy%20or%20sell%2C%20trading%20shares%20of%20private%20companies%20is%20much%20more%20opaque%2C%20requiring%20middlemen%20and%20weeks%20of%20time%20to%20finalize.%20Sellers%20are%20usually%20employees%20or%20early%20investors%20looking%20to%20cash%20out%2C%20while%20buyers%20include%20VCs%2C%20family%20offices%2C%20and%20hedge%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEveryone%20is%20fighting%20to%20get%20shares%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20secondary%20broker%20who%20declined%20to%20be%20identified%20for%20fear%20of%20alienating%20Anduril.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20frenzy%20to%20get%20shares.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%20six%20months%2C%20Anduril%20has%20climbed%20from%20fifth%20to%20fourth%20on%20the%20rankings%20of%20companies%20with%20the%20most%20order%20volume%20(behind%20only%20SpaceX%2C%20ByteDance%2C%20and%20OpenAI)%20on%20Caplight%2C%20a%20private%20market%20exchange%20for%20shares%20of%20startups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Caplight%2C%20buyers%20are%20willing%20to%20buy%20Anduril%20shares%20at%20%3Cspan%3E%2456.67%20per%20share%2C%20which%20is%3C%2Fspan%3E%20an%20implied%20valuation%20of%20%2436.3%20billion%2C%20a%2063%25%20increase%20over%20the%20past%20six%20months.%20The%20company%20last%20raised%20financing%20last%20summer%20at%20a%20valuation%20of%20%2414%20billion%2C%20or%20%3Cspan%3E%2421.74%20per%20share%2C%20per%20Caplight.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2025%2F02%2F07%2Fanduril-in-talks-to-raise-money-at-28-billion-valuation.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20CNBC%20report%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20Anduril%20was%20in%20talks%20to%20double%20the%20company's%20valuation%20to%20%2428%20billion%20led%20to%20more%20interest%2C%20according%20to%20Greg%20Martin%2C%20managing%20director%20and%20co-founder%20of%20Rainmaker%20Securities%2C%20a%20secondary%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20we%20started%20hearing%20about%20the%20new%20round%2C%20we%20started%20to%20see%20new%20bids%20come%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20Martin%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20have%20anything%20to%20add%20to%20CNBC's%20reporting%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20an%20Anduril%20spokesperson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ff011952-b1b9-48e8-bc5b-038ac8ddcf43%5C%22%3EAnduril%20shares%20are%20hard%20to%20find%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20all%20that%20demand%2C%20few%20deals%20are%20actually%20being%20completed%20because%2C%20like%20many%20private%20companies%2C%20Anduril%20tightly%20controls%20its%20own%20stock.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnduril's%20common%20stock%20is%20subject%20to%20transfer%20restrictions%2C%20and%20we%20don't%20allow%20secondary%20transactions%2C%26quot%3B%20explained%20the%20Anduril%20spokesperson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20buyers%20have%20been%20skirting%20the%20company's%20rules%20by%20buying%20stock%20in%20special-purpose%20vehicles%20(SPVs)%2C%20a%20financial%20structure%20that%20allows%20a%20group%20of%20investors%20to%20pool%20their%20funds%2C%20that%20operate%20in%20a%20gray%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESydecar%2C%20an%20SPV%20and%20fund%20administration%20platform%2C%20saw%20greater%20volume%20in%20Anduril%20SPV%20deals%20transacted%20by