2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fwhatsapp-for-ios-tests-spotify-integration-for-music-sharing-how-it-works-125032500577_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22ATM%20Withdrawals%20To%20Get%20Costlier%20From%20May%201%3A%20Check%20New%20Charges%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20often%20withdraw%20cash%20from%20an%20ATM%2C%20be%20prepared%20to%20pay%20a%20bit%20extra%20starting%20May%201.%20This%20comes%20after%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20(RBI)%20approved%20a%20hike%20in%20ATM%20interchange%20fees%2C%20the%20amount%20a%20bank%20pays%20to%20another%20for%20using%20its%20services%2C%20including%20the%20expense%20of%20owning%20an%20ATM.%20Apart%20from%20that%2C%20it%20also%20includes%20charges%20for%20offering%20exclusive%20services%20to%20a%20cardholder%20of%20another%20bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECash%20withdrawal%20fee%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Rs%2017%20to%20Rs%2019%20per%20transaction%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBalance%20inquiry%20fee%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Rs%206%20to%20Rs%207%20per%20transaction%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEffective%20from%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20May%201%2C%202025%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20financial%20transactions%20get%20expensive%20by%20Rs%202%2C%20the%20non-financial%20transactions%2C%20such%20as%20balance%20inquiries%2C%20will%20cost%20an%20extra%20rupee%20from%20May%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hiked%20fees%20are%20a%20component%20of%20an%20RBI-authorised%20revision%20based%20on%20a%20National%20Payments%20Corporation%20of%20India%20(NPCI)%20recommendation.%20White-label%20ATM%20operators%20had%20been%20pushing%20for%20a%20raise%2C%20claiming%20the%20previous%20fees%20were%20unaffordable%20in%20light%20of%20growing%20operating%20expenses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RBI-approved%20revised%20fees%20will%20soon%20become%20the%20new%20standard%2C%20Business%20Today%20reported.%20RBI%20has%20yet%20to%20publish%20an%20official%20notification%20ab