have%20come%20as%20job%20opportunities%20for%20software%20engineers%20%E2%80%94%20a%20historically%20well-paid%20job%20%E2%80%94%20have%20plummeted.%20On%20Indeed%2C%20openings%20in%20the%20US%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjobs-software-engineers-coders-bad-market-ai-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edown%20a%20third%20from%20five%20years%20ago%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20raises%20a%20big%20question%3A%20how%20can%20software%20engineers%20not%20just%20survive%20but%20thrive%20in%20the%20vibe%20coding%20era%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20spoke%20to%20software%20engineers%20who%20said%20vibe%20coding%20doesn't%20have%20to%20mean%20total%20doom%20for%20career%20prospects%20%E2%80%94%20so%20long%20as%20they%20prioritize%20these%20three%20skills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2235204b4c-4fa1-47a3-9c3e-3a7f623c8a12%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Embrace%20the%20vibes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEmbracing%20and%20mastering%20vibe%20coding%20tools%20is%20a%20good%20place%20to%20start.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChatGPT%2C%20Cursor%2C%20Replit%2C%20and%20Windsurf%20are%20just%20some%20of%20the%20tools%20being%20used%20to%20fast-track%20workloads.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMarc%20Tuscher%2C%20chief%20technology%20officer%20at%20AI%20robotics%20firm%20Sereact%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20vibe%20coding%20tools%20make%20him%20%26quot%3Bmuch%20faster%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20is%20why%20he%20encourages%20his%20team%20of%20roughly%2025%20software%20engineers%20to%20use%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20Tuscher%20acknowledges%20these%20tools%20can%20make%20mistakes%20that%20need%20to%20be%20debugged%2C%20he%20says%20a%20software%20engineer%20working%20with%20AI%20tools%20will%20have%20an%20advantage%20over%20one%20that%20doesn't.%20%26quot%3BThe%20amount%20of%20speed%20you%20can%20get%20compared%20to%20coding%20yourself%20is%20crazy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20part%20of%20the%20reason%20industry%20leaders%20have%20become%20more%20vocal%20about%20putting%20these%20tools%20to%20use.%20Sam%20Altman%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20OpenAI%2C%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20Stratechery's%20Ben%20Thompson%20this%20month%20that%20for%20students%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-ai-coding-job-market-software-engineer-students-openai-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bthe%20obvious%20tactical%20thing%20is%20just%20get%20really%20good%20at%20using%20AI%20tools.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sam%20Altman%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F679d36f77bb3f854015b6416%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223999%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESam%20Altman%20is%20encouraging%20students%20to%20use%20AI%20tools.%3Cp%3EMichael%20M.%20Santiago%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETanay%20Kothari%2C%20CEO%20of%20Wispr%20Flow%2C%20a%20voice%20agent%20that%20can%20be%20used%20to%20input%20commands%20into%20vibe%20coding%20tools%20like%20Cursor%2C%20understands%20that%20there%20might%20be%20some%20reluctance%20among%20veteran%20developers%20to%20embrace%20such%20tools.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20experience%2C%20however%2C%20engineers%20who%20think%20they're%20%26quot%3Bjust%20really%20good%26quot%3B%20will%20start%20seeing%20vibe%20coding%20tools%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Bunlock%26quot%3B%20once%20they%20understand%20the%20efficiency%20gains%20at%20hand.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20who%20use%20AI%20tools%20roughly%20get%20twice%20as%20much%20done%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22340de5aa-7704-401c-aee3-30adc7f6fb23%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Up%20your%20prompt%20game%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELearning%20how%20to%20give%20instructions%20%E2%80%94%20known%20as%20prompts%20%E2%80%94%20to%20vibe%20coding%20tools%20in%20a%20smarter%20way%20can%20also%20give%20engineers%20an%20edge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20hottest%20new%20programming%20language%20is%20English%2C%26quot%3B%20Karpathy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fkarpathy%2Fstatus%2F1617979122625712128%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Equipped%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20January%202023%2C%20just%20a%20few%20months%20after%20ChatGPT's%20first%20public%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResearch%20papers%2C%20such%20as%20the%20original%20paper%20behind%20OpenAI's%20GPT-3%2C%20suggest%20that%20the%20large%20language%20models%20powering%20today's%20generative%20AI%20tools%20can%2C%20as%20Karpathy%20put%20it%2C%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fkarpathy%2Fstatus%2F1627366413840322562%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3B'programmed'%20inside%20the%20prompt.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20a%20carefully%20constructed%20prompt%20can%20drastically%20alter%20the%20quality%20of%20output%20for%20an%20AI%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223701%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Andrej%20Karpathy%20wearing%20a%20black%20sweater%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66fd43d35ccfc192a5528289%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222991%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAndrej%20Karpathy%20captured%20the%20AI%20coding%20zeitgeist%20with%20%26quot%3Bvibe%20coding.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ESan%20Francisco%20Chronicle%2FHearst%20Newspapers%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20why%20Ash%20Edwards%2C%20a%20former%20Palantir%20engineer%20turned%20CEO%20of%20AI%20agent%20company%20Fern%20Labs%2C%20sees%20software%20engineers%20getting%20more%20value%20out%20of%20vibe%20coding%20tools%20by%20being%20more%20%26quot%3Bprescriptive.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20real%20failure%20case%20is%20almost%20letting%20the%20code%20choose%20its%20own%20directions%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20you%20can%20usually%20get%20much%20better%20results%20if%20you%20know%20what%20you%20want%20to%20do%20and%20you%20know%20roughly%20how%20you%20want%20to%20build%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20view%20shared%20by%20Kothari%3A%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20right%20set%20of%20questions%20to%20ask%20ChatGPT%20to%20get%20your%20work%20done.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b6cb7f8c-8386-460a-bf71-e23fb666c2c8%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20A%20clear-thinking%20mindset%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20AI%20is%20doing%20more%20of%20the%20grunt%20work%20of%20software%20development%2C%20what%20should%20engineers%20focus%20their%20newfound%20extra%20time%20on%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESoftware%20experts%20who%20spoke%20to%20BI%20said%20the%20answer%20was%20simple%3A%20focus%20on%20thinking%20clearly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcareer-ladder-software-engineers-collapsing-ai-google-meta-coding-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esoftware%20engineers%3C%2Fa%3E%20build%20programs%20and%20apps%2C%20they%20spend%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20thinking%20carefully%20about%20what%20exactly%20is%20being%20built%20and%20how%20it%20might%20be%20stitched%20together%20in%20a%20wider%20system.%20This%20all%20requires%20careful%20thinking%20before%20lines%20of%20code%20are%20even%20written.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20type%20of%20thinking%20that%20helps%20this%20process%20is%20reasoning%20from%20%26quot%3Bfirst%20principles%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20Wispr%20Flow's%20Kothari%2C%20referring%20to%20breaking%20a%20complex%20problem%20into%20smaller%20pieces%20to%20find%20a%20suitable%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20is%20a%20very%20hard%2C%20high-level%20problem%20that%20you%20need%20to%20be%20able%20to%20solve%20regardless%20of%20how%20good%20AI%20gets%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKothari%20notes%20that%20this%20is%20a%20key%20attribute%20of%20what%20defines%20a%20%26quot%3B10x%20engineer%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20an%20industry%20archetype%20of%20an%20engineer%20who%20is%20typically%2010%20times%20more%20productive%20and%20valuable%20than%20their%20counterparts.%20%26quot%3B10x%20things%20come%20from%20clarity%20of%20thought%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThinking%20about%20systems%20at%20large%20is%20another%20helpful%20way%20to%20approach%20software%20engineering%20problems.%20Kothari%20notes%20that%20people%20can%20waste%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20not%20doing%20this%2C%20as%20it%20can%20lead%20to%20building%20%26quot%3Bthe%20wrong%20thing%20that%20nobody%20really%20wanted.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFern%20Labs'%20Edwards%20agrees%2C%20noting%20that%20engineers%20are%20%26quot%3Balways%20going%20to%20need%20to%20be%20able%20to%20think%20about%20systems%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20despite%20the%20growing%20use%20of%20vibe%20coding%20tools%20%E2%80%94%20as%20they%20will%20fundamentally%20still%20be%20the%20ones%20needing%20to%20oversee%20a%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHaving%20that%20software%20engineering%20mindset%2C%20understanding%20how%20to%20think%20about%20problems%20and%20break%20them%20down%20and%20think%20about%20them%20in%20abstraction%20%E2%80%94%20I%20think%20that's%20always%20going%20to%20be%20useful%20and%20important%2C%20if%20not%20more%20so%2C%20as%20these%20things%20get%20more%20and%20more%20powerful%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvibe-coding-software-engineer-skills-jobs-ai-cursor-chatgpt-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742891401000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67e26639b8b41a9673fb984a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvibe-coding-software-engineer-skills-jobs-ai-cursor-chatgpt-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20vibe%20coding%20era%2C%20in%20which%20AI%20is%20automating%20more%20of%20the%20work%20of%20software%20engineers%2C%20is%20raising%20questions%20about%20which%20skills%20really%20matter.%22%2C%22author%22%3A