247%20to%20%2410%20on%20your%20order%2C%20and%20then%20maybe%20you%20have%20to%20pay%20an%20overdraft%20fee%20because%20of%20a%20cash%20flow%20issue%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Nadine%20Chabrier%2C%20the%20senior%20policy%20counsel%20at%20the%20Center%20for%20Responsible%20Lending.%20%26quot%3BSo%20you%20could%20really%20balloon%20the%20amount%20of%20money%20you%20pay%20for%20just%20one%20thing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EFood%20delivery%20with%20companies%20such%20as%20DoorDash%2C%20Uber%20Eats%2C%20and%20GrubHub%20has%20become%20a%20weirdly%20controversial%20topic%20on%20the%20internet%20over%20the%20past%20few%20years.%20The%20kerfuffle%20is%20always%20the%20same%3A%20Someone%20posts%20something%20about%20all%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoordash-regulatory-response-fee-nyc-minimum-wage-law-delivery-workers-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edelivery%20fees%3C%2Fa%3E%20making%20their%20order%20extra%20expensive%2C%20someone%20else%20says%20they%20should%20just%20go%20pick%20it%20up%20or%20cook%20for%20themselves%2C%20and%20then%20everybody%20yells%20about%20whether%20it's%20offensive%20because%20some%20people%20can't%20leave%20their%20homes%20or%20cook%20or%20some%20other%20protest.%20On%20this%20DoorDash-Klarna%20announcement%2C%20you%20can%20already%20hear%20a%20similar%20argument%3A%20What%20about%20people%20who%20can't%20afford%20that%20burrito%20right%20this%20second%20but%20really%20need%20(OK%2C%20want)%20it%20and%20for%20whatever%20reason%20don't%20feel%20that%20they%20have%20another%20option%3F%20I%20posed%20this%20question%20to%20every%20expert%20I%20talked%20to%2C%20and%20the%20answer%20was%20mainly%2C%20sure%20if%20you%20want%20to%20do%20this%2C%20go%20ahead%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20in%20your%20best%20interest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20have%20the%20free%20will%20to%20make%20a%20choice%20of%20the%20way%20in%20which%20they%20want%20to%20pay%20for%20something%2C%20but%20there%20may%20be%20unintended%20consequences%2C%26quot%3B%20Chabrier%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDoorDash%20and%20Klarna%20will%20%26quot%3Bundoubtedly%20tout%20the%20idea%20of%2C%20'Well%20if%20you%20pay%20for%20it%20in%20four%20payments%2C%20it's%20the%20same%20as%20up%20front%2C'%20but%20we're%20not%20talking%20about%20major%20purchases%20where%20that's%20going%20to%20save%20you%20any%20type%20of%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20Lawless%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBreaking%20up%20large%20payments%20for%20goods%20that%20we're%20going%20to%20use%20for%20years%20can%20make%20sense.%20You%20buy%20a%20house%20on%20a%20mortgage%20so%20you%20can%20pay%20it%20off%20over%20years%20as%20the%20value%20(hopefully)%20goes%20up.%20You%20get%20a%20car%20loan%20so%20you%20can%20pay%20it%20down%20every%20month%20with%20the%20money%20you%20make%20driving%20to%20and%20from%20work.%20Paying%20down%20larger%20purchases%20over%20time%20frees%20up%20cash%20for%20other%20needs%2C%20or%20for%20investments%20that%20will%20grow%20over%20time.%20But%20a%20quick%20food%20order%20may%20not%20fall%20into%20this%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20good%20economic%20case%20for%20financing%20investments%20over%20the%20long%20term%2C%20and%20we%20have%20stretched%20the%20definition%20of%20durable%20goods%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20ways%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Michael%20Madowitz%2C%20an%20economist%20at%20the%20Roosevelt%20Institute%2C%20a%20progressive%20think%20tank.%20%26quot%3BDelivered%20food%20may%20in%20fact%20be%20the%20least%20durable%20good%20we've%20tried%20this%20with.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20backlash%20to%20the%20announcement%2C%20Klarna%20and%20DoorDash%20are%20trying%20to%20emphasize%20their%20partnership%20is%20about%20more%20than%20burritos.%20In%20an%20emailed%20statement%2C%20a%20DoorDash%20spokesperson%20said%20the%20company's%20customers%20already%20had%20%26quot%3Bplenty%20of%20ways%20to%20pay%26quot%3B%20including%20PayPal%2C%20Venmo%2C%20SNAP%2FEBT%2C%20and%20credit%20cards%2C%20and%20added%20that%20this%20option%20wasn't%20just%20for%20food%20orders.%20%26quot%3BWith%20over%2025%25%20of%20customers%20now%20shopping%20beyond%20restaurants%20in%20categories%20like%20retail%2C%20beauty%2C%20and%20home%20improvement%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20it's%20the%20gaming%20console%20or%20laptop%20for%20your%20kids%2C%20the%20new%20barbecue%20ahead%20of%20summer%20grilling%20season%2C%20or%20the%20running%20shoes%20you%20need%20for%20tomorrow's%205K%20%E2%80%94%20this%20partnership%20provides%20even%20more%20flexibility%2C%20control%2C%20and%20options%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%20They%20also%20pointed%20to%20a%20Klarna%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.klarna.com%2Finternational%2Fpress%2Fconvenience-shouldnt-cost-how-klarna-puts-consumers-first%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eblog%20post%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20the%20deal.%20A%20Klarna%20spokesperson%20said%20the%20partnership%20was%20%26quot%3Bespecially%20important%20as%20DoorDash%20expands%20its%20offering%20into%20electronics%2C%20big-box%20retail%2C%20and%20gifts.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20partnership%20isn't%20the%20end%20of%20the%20world%20in%20terms%20of%20signaling%20some%20sea%20change%20in%20consumer%20credit%3B%20nor%20is%20it%20a%20sign%20that%20a%20recession%20is%20here.%20These%20companies%20are%20offering%20people%20more%20ways%20to%20pay%20so%20they'll%20buy%20more%2C%20perhaps%2C%20than%20they%20had%20planned.%20This%20is%20a%20way%20to%20squeeze%20more%20cash%20out%20of%20consumers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20happening%20at%20a%20moment%20when%20the%20cops%20who%20are%20supposed%20to%20be%20on%20the%20consumer%20beat%20%E2%80%94%20the%20CFPB%20%E2%80%94%20may%20not%20be%20doing%20much%2C%20Madowitz%20noted%2C%20given%20the%20current%20White%20House%20administration's%20hands-off%20bent.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%20if%20this%20is%20the%20kind%20of%20thing%20CFPB%2C%20SEC%2C%20or%20both%20should%20have%20a%20very%20close%20eye%20on%2C%20and%20maybe%20we%20j