0show%20sales%20are%20slumping%20in%20multiple%20markets%2C%20including%20the%20US%2C%20where%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-latest-place-tesla-sales-plunging-elon-musk-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enew%20Tesla%20registrations%3C%2Fa%3E%20fell%20by%2011%25%20in%20January%2C%20based%20on%20data%20from%20S%26amp%3BP%20Global%20Mobility.%20In%20Europe%2C%20registrations%20fell%20across%2025%20European%20markets%20by%20an%20average%20of%2044%25%20in%20February%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jato.com%2Fresources%2Fmedia-and-press-releases%2Feuropean-registrations-of-chinese-car-brands-soar-in-january-while-tesla-sales-nosedive%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJATO%20Dynamics%3C%2Fa%3E%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcybertruck-owners-tesla-takedown-protest-harassment-vandalism-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETesla%20owners%3C%2Fa%3E%20told%20BI%20the%20protests%20have%20strengthened%20their%20support%20for%20Musk%20%E2%80%94%20one%20analyst%20suggested%20recently%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-stock-elon-musk-politics-sales-selloff-upgrade-ev-trump-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ered%20states%20could%20help%20salvage%20the%20company's%20sales%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Many%20others%20are%20choosing%20to%20add%20anti-Elon%20stickers%20to%20their%20vehicles%20or%20ditch%20them%20entirely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScott%20Oran%2C%20a%20real%20estate%20developer%20from%20the%20Boston%20area%2C%20said%20he%20sold%20his%20Tesla%20in%20February%20%26quot%3Bas%20a%20protest%26quot%3B%20against%20Elon%20Musk%20and%20his%20work%20at%20DOGE.%20Another%20Tesla%20Model%203%20owner%2C%20who%20asked%20to%20remain%20anonymous%2C%20said%20they%20decided%20to%20sell%20for%20fear%20that%20Musk's%20political%20activities%20could%20cause%20Tesla's%20plummeting%20resale%20values%20to%20drop%20even%20furthe