uvenation%20of%20the%20Yamuna%20River%2C%20inspired%20by%20the%20Sabarmati%20riverfront%20project.%20The%20government%20has%20allocated%20Rs%20500%20crore%20for%20Yamuna%20cleaning%2C%20ensuring%20that%20only%20treated%20water%20enters%20the%20river%20through%20the%20decentralization%20of%2040%20sewage%20treatment%20plants%20(STPs).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20Rs%20500%20crore%20has%20been%20earmarked%20for%20the%20repair%20and%20upgradation%20of%20STPs%2C%20and%20Rs%20250%20crore%20for%20replacing%20old%20sewer%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20major%20focus%20has%20also%20been%20placed%20on%20clean%20drinking%20water%20and%20sanitation%2C%20with%20Rs%209%2C000%20crore%20allocated%20for%20related%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20health%20sector%20has%20been%20allocated%20Rs%206%2C874%20crore%2C%20with%20a%20focus%20on%20setting%20up%20health%20and%20wellness%20centres%20and%20expanding%20the%20Ayushman%20Arogya%20Mandir%20initiative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20government%20has%20allocated%20Rs%201%2C000%20crore%20for%20improved%20transport%20links%20within%20Delhi-NCR.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20women's%20welfare%2C%20Rs%205%2C100%20crore%20has%20been%20earmarked%20to%20provide%20Rs%202%2C500%20per%20month%20to%20eligible%20women.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20government%20will%20install%2050%2C000%20CCTV%20cameras%20across%20the%20city%20to%20enhance%20women's%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Gupta%20announced%20that%20the%20government%20aims%20to%20make%20Delhi%20an%20investment-%20and%20innovation-friendly%20city.%20To%20achieve%20this%2C%20a%20new%20industrial%20policy%20and%20a%20new%20warehouse%20policy%20will%20be%20introduced.%20A%20Traders'%20Welfare%20Board%20will%20also%20be%20established.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20Delhi%20will%20host%20its%20first-ever%20Global%20Investment%20Summit%2C%20which%20will%20be%20held%20every%20two%20years.%20To%20support%20small-scale%20industries%2C%20Rs%2050%20crore%20has%20been%20earmarked%20for%20skill%20development%20programs%2C%20including%20bee-keeping.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20also%20allocated%20Rs%20696%20crore%20for%20the%20development%20of%20slum%20clusters%20and%20Rs%20100%20crore%20to%20set%20up%20100%20Atal%20Canteens%20across%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20difference%20between%20us%20and%20them%20(AAP).%20%26quot%3BYou%20(AAP)%20made%20'Sheesh%20Mahal'%20for%20yourself%2C%20we%20will%20build%20houses%20for%20the%20poor.%20You%20installed%20pot%20toilets%20worth%20lakhs%2C%20we%20will%20make%20toilets%20for%20the%20people%20in%20slum%20areas%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20education%2C%20Ms%20Gupta%20attacked%20the%20previous%20AAP%20government%2C%20accusing%20it%20of%20misleading%20people%20about%20the%20quality%20of%20education.%20%26quot%3BThe%20AAP%20government%20failed%20many%20students%20in%209th%20and%2011th%20standard%20so%20that%20their%2010th%20and%2012th%20results%20appear%20better%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20reform%20the%20education%20system%2C%20the%20government%20will%20launch%20CM%20SHRI%20Schools%2C%20inspired%20by%20PM%20SHRI%20Schools%20and%20aligned%20with%20the%20New%20Education%20Policy.%20The%20FY26%20Budget%20has%20allocated%20Rs%20100%20crore%20for%20these%20schools.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20Delhi%20government%20will%20provide%20free%20laptops%20to%201%2C200%20students%20passing%20class%2010th%20and%20has%20allocated%20Rs%20750%20crore%20for%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Gupta%20also%20announced%20a%20new%20education%20hub%20in%20the%20Narela%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20Budget%20is%20the%20first%20presented%20by%20a%20BJP-led%20government%20in%20Delhi%20in%20over%2026%20years%2C%20following%20the%20party's%20victory%20over%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20in%20last%20month's%20Assembly%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20e