0portfolio%20and%20provide%20'greater%20access%20to%20credit%20for%20individuals%20and%20businesses'%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fsmfg-raises-175-million-through-ecb-facility-on-fully-hedged-basis-125032500464_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jeffrey%20Goldberg%3A%20The%20Journalist%20Who%20Was%20Mistakenly%20Sent%20US%20War%20Plans%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETop%20Trump%20administration%20officials%20mistakenly%20added%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhite-house-officials-accidentally-shared-yemen-war-plans-with-journalist-8003397%5C%22%3EJeffrey%20Goldberg%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20The%20%3Cem%3EAtlantic%3C%2Fem%3E's%20editor-in-chief%2C%20to%20an%20encrypted%20Signal%20chat%20discussing%20military%20strikes%20on%20Yemen's%20Iran-backed%20Houthis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chat%20group%2C%20titled%20%26quot%3BHouthi%20PC%20small%20group%2C%26quot%3B%20included%20US%20Vice%20President%20JD%20Vance%2C%20Secretary%20of%20Defence%20Pete%20Hegseth%2C%20and%20National%20Security%20Adviser%20Mike%20Waltz.%20According%20to%20Goldberg%2C%20Waltz%20directed%20his%20deputy%2C%20Alex%20Wong%2C%20to%20form%20a%20%26quot%3Btiger%20team%26quot%3B%20to%20coordinate%20strikes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Goldberg%20called%20the%20incident%20a%20%26quot%3Bshocking%20reckless%26quot%3B%20security%20blunder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20is%20Jeffery%20Goldberg%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EJeffrey%20Goldberg%20was%20born%20in%20Brooklyn%2C%20New%20York.%20Mr%20Goldberg%2C%20a%20Jew%2C%20grew%20up%20in%20Malverne%2C%20Long%20Island.%20He%20attended%20the%20University%20of%20Pennsylvania%2C%20where%20he%20was%20editor-in-chief%20of%20The%20Daily%20Pennsylvanian.%20He%20now%20lives%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20with%20his%20wife%2C%20Pamela%20Reeves.%20The%20couple%20has%20three%20children.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHe%20left%20college%20to%20move%20to%20Israel.%20During%20the%20First%20Intifada%2C%20he%20served%20in%20the%20Israel%20Defence%20Forces%20(IDF)%20as%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2F%C2%A0https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2006%2F10%2F28%2Fbooks%2F28bron.html%C2%A0%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20prison%20guard%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20Ktzi'ot%20Prison.%20There%2C%20he%20met%20Rafiq%20Hijazi%2C%20a%20PLO%20(Palestine%20Liberation%20Organisation)%20leader%2C%20whom%20he%20described%20as%20the%20only%20Palestinian%20in%20the%20prison%20who%20understood%20Zionism.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20Israel%2C%20he%20worked%20as%20a%20columnist%20for%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Jerusalem%20Post.%3C%2Fem%3E%20After%20returning%20to%20the%20US%2C%20he%20started%20as%20a%20reporter%20at%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Washington%20Post.%3C%2Fem%3E%20He%20later%20became%20the%20New%20York%20bureau%20chief%20of%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Forward%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20a%20contributing%20editor%20at%20%3Cem%3ENew%20York%20Magazine.%20%3C%2Fem%3EHe%20also%20contributed%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%20Magazine%3C%2Fem%3E.%20In%202000%2C%20he%20joined%20%3Cem%3EThe%20New%20Yorker.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%202001%2C%20he%20was%20a%20fellow%20of%20the%20Jerusalem%20Foundation%2C%20and%20in%202002%2C%20he%20served%20as%20a%20public%20policy%20scholar%20at%20the%20Woodrow%20Wilson%20International%20Centre%20for%20Scholars.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%202007%2C%20David%20G%20Bradley%20convinced%20him%20to%20write%20for%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Atlantic%20%3C%2Fem%3Eafter%20nearly%20two%20years%20of%20persuasion.%20In%202011%2C%20he%20became%20a%20columnist%20at%20%3Cem%3EBloomberg%20View%3C%2Fem%3E%20but%20left%20in%202014.%20In%202016%2C%20he%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2016%2F10%2F12%2Fbusiness%2Fatlantic-is-expected-to-name-jeffrey-goldberg-its-editor-in-chief.html%3F_r%3D0%C2%A0%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebecame%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Atlantic%3C%2Fem%3E's%20editor-in-chief%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20August%202023%2C%20he%20became%20the%20moderator%20of%20%3Cem%3EPBS's%20Washington%20Week%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20was%20rebranded%20as%20%3Cem%3EWashington%20Week%3C%2Fem%3E%20with%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Atlantic.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMr%20Goldberg%20has%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.americanacademy.de%2Fperson%2Fjeffrey-goldberg%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%20from%20conflict%20zones%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20Afghanistan%2C%20Pakistan%2C%20Syria%2C%20and%20the%20Palestinian%20territories.%20He%20once%20lived%20in%20a%20Taliban%20madrasa%20for%20a%20month%20and%20has%20interviewed%20leaders%20of%20groups%20such%20as%20Hezbollah%2C%20Hamas%2C%20al-Qaeda%2C%20and%20the%20Taliban.%20He%20also%20covered%20the%20Second%20Persian%20Gulf%20War%20from%20inside%20Iraq%20for%20The%20New%20Yorker.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EJeffrey%20Goldberg%20has%20received%20several%20prestigious%20journalism%20awards%2C%20including%20the%20Overseas%20Press%20Club%20Award%20for%20best%20human-rights%20reporting%20and%20the%20Abraham%20Cahan%20Prize%20in%20Journalism.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJeffrey%20Goldberg%20said%20in%20a%20report%20on%20Monday%20that%20he%20was%20unexpectedly%20invited%20on%20March%2013%20to%20the%20encrypted%20chat%20group%20on%20Signal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20world%20found%20out%20shortly%20before%202%20p.m.%20eastern%20time%20on%20March%2015%20that%20the%20United%20States%20was%20bombing%20Houthi%20targets%20across%20Yemen.%20I%2C%20however%2C%20knew%20two%20hours%20before%20the%20first%20bombs%20exploded%20that%20the%20attack%20might%20be%20coming.%20The%20reason%20I%20knew%20this%20is%20that%20Pete%20Hegseth%2C%20the%20secretary%20of%20defense%2C%20had%20texted%20me%20the%20war%20plan%20at%2011%3A44%20a.m.%20The%20plan%20included%20precise%20information%20about%20weapons%20packages%2C%20targets%2C%20and%20timing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742886720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F1m9ee1ho_jeffrey-goldberg_625x300_25_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjeffrey-goldberg-the-journalist-who-was-mistakenly-sent-us-yemen-war-plans-8005248%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Top%20Trump%20administration%20officials%20mistakenly%20added%20Jeffrey%20Goldberg%2C%20The%20Atlantic's%20editor-in-chief%2C%20to%20an%20encrypted%20Signal%20chat%20discussing%20military%20strikes%20on%20Houthis.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjeffrey-goldberg-the-journalist-who-was-mistakenly-sent-us-yemen-war-plans-8005248%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Hangry%20Petz%E2%80%99%20Animated%20Series%20Coming%20From%20Toonz%2C%20Jay%40Play%20Partnership%20(EXCLUSIVE)%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742886660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FHangry-Petz.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236347210%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Toonz%20Media%20Group%20has%20partnered%20with%20toy%20manufacturer%20Jay%40Play%20to%20develop%20%E2%80%9CHangry%20Petz%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20new%20CGI-animated%20series%20created%20exclusively%20for%20digital%20platforms.%20The%20project%20will%20consist%20of%2026%20three-minute%20episodes%20featuring%20characters%20inspired%20by%20Jay%40Play%E2%80%99s%20successful%20stuffed%20toy%20line%2C%20which%20has%20already%20generated%20buzz%20through%20social%20media%20campaigns.%20The%20show%E2%80%99s%20storyline%20centers%20on%20Bella%2C%20a%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Naman%20Ramachandran%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2025%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fhangry-petz-animated-series-1236347210%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22CBFC%20suggests%20these%20cuts%20for%20Sikandar%20-%20more%20deets%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742886532000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-119465118%2Cimgsize-30750.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fcbfc-has-suggested-these-cuts-in-salman-khans-sikandar-duration-certificate-and-other-details-inside%2Farticleshow%2F119464958.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F119464958.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ESalman%20Khan's%20upcoming%20Eid%20release%2C%20'Sikandar'%2C%20directed%20by%20AR%20Murugadoss%20and%20co-starring%20Rashmika%20Mandanna%2C%20has%20received%20a%20U%2FA%20certificate%20with%20minor%20cuts%20from%20the%20CBFC.%20Despite%20his%20rib%20injury%2C%20Salman%20performed%20intense%20action%20scenes.%20The%20film%20releases%20on%20March%2030%20and%20has%20a%20runtime%20of%202%20hours%2030%20minutes.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fcbfc-has-suggested-these-cuts-in-salman-khans-sikandar-duration-certificate-and-other-details-inside%2Farticleshow%2F119464958.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20UGC's%20Latest%20Caste%20Rules%3A%20When%20The%20Cure%20Worsens%20A%20Disease%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20malaise%20of%20casteism%20took%20the%20lives%20of%20Rohith%20Vemula%20and%20Payal%20Tadvi.%20Their%20parents%20have%20pleaded%20with%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%20to%20treat%20this%20malaise%20on%20campuses.%20If%20they%20needed%20medical%20advice%20on%20the%20inefficacy%20of%20an%20existing%20treatment%20for%20a%20physical%20malaise%2C%20then%20the%20physician%20may%20have%20mistakenly%20recommended%20something%20less%20effective%20to%20them.%20This%20is%20the%20case%20with%20the%20University%20Grants%20Commission's%20(UGC)%20response%20to%20the%20parents%20of%20Rohith%20Vemula%20and%20Payal%20Tadvi%20by%20proposing%20the%202025%20draft%20regulations%20on%20equity.%20The%20draft%20tapers%20down%20the%20existing%20regulations%20of%202012%20as%20it%20narrows%20the%20definition%20of%20caste-based%20discrimination%2C%20adopting%20a%20non-intersectional%20approach%2C%20and%20dispensing%20with%20commonly%20recurring%20situations%20of%20discrimination%20and%20the%20effects%20thereof.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Even%20Is%20Discrimination%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202025%20regulations%20define%20discrimination%20as%20%E2%80%9Cunfair%2C%20differential%2C%20or%20biased%20treatment%20or%20any%20such%20act%20against%20any%20stakeholder%20on%20the%20grounds%20only%20of%20religion%2C%20race%2C%20caste%2C%20sex%2C%20place%20of%20birth%2C%20or%20any%20of%20them%E2%80%9D.%20The%20isolated%20definition%20of%20caste-based%20discrimination%20as%20%E2%80%9Conly%20against%20the%20members%20of%20the%20scheduled%20castes%20and%20scheduled%20tribes%E2%80%9D%20excludes%20the%20broader%20ways%20in%20which%20it%20operates.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20a%20dairy%20caste%20Gujjar%20student%20may%20be%20denied%20entry%20into%20a%20sponsorships%20and%20accounts-keeping%20committee%20on%20the%20assumption%20of%20being%20unreliable%20and%20unworthy%20of%20trust.%20In%20contrast%2C%20a%20trader%20caste%20Vaish%20student%20may%20be%20preferred%20on%20the%20assumption%20that%20Vaish%20people%20are%20good%20with%20money.%20A%20priestly%20caste%20Brahmin%20student%20may%20be%20placed%20in%20a%20supervisory%20role%20on%20the%20assumption%20that%20Brahmins%20are%20morally%20upright%20and%20trustworthy.%20As%20much%20as%20this%20is%20caste-based%20discrimination%2C%20it%20would%20not%20be%20addressed%20in%20the%202025%20draft%20regulations%20despite%20Gujjar%20being%20a%20protected%20legal%20category%20of%20Backward%20Classes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20'Non-Intersectional'%20Approach%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202025%20draft%20wording%20%E2%80%9Con%20the%20grounds%20only%20of%E2%80%9D%20has%20served%20as%20the%20rationale%20for%20non-intersectional%20interpretations.%20In%201981%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%20ruled%20that%20the%20alleged%20discrimination%20against%20air%20hostesses%20was%20not%20%E2%80%9Con%20grounds%20only%20of%E2%80%9D%20sex%20because%20of%20other%20factors%20that%20also%20constituted%20the%20category%20of%20air%20hostesses.%20This%20court%20ruling%20has%20established%20a%20non-intersectional%20approach%20to%20reading%20the%20given%20categories%E2%80%94of%20religion%2C%20race%2C%20caste%2C%20sex%2C%20place%20of%20birth%E2%80%94in%20Article%2015%20of%20the%20Constitution.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COr%E2%80%9D%20places%20a%20mutual%20exclusivity%20in%20the%20given%20categories.%20It%20can%20be%20caste%20or%20sex%2C%20it%20cannot%20be%20both.%20The%202012%20regulations%20facilitate%20the%20possibility%20of%20intersectional%20reading%20by%20replacing%20%3Cem%3Eor%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewith%20%3Cem%3Eand%3C%2Fem%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9Cbased%20on%20caste%2C%20creed%2C%20religion%2C%20language%2C%20ethnicity%2C%20gender%20and%20disabilities.%E2%80%9D%20The%20prospects%20of%20the%20words%20%E2%80%9Cor%20any%20of%20them%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%202025%20draft%20could%20be%20interpreted%20as%20the%20intersectional%20operation%20of%20given%20categories.%20It's%20a%20distant%20possibility%20contingent%20on%20the%20courts%20making%20this%20kind%20of%20interpretation.%20Until%20then%2C%20women%20and%20LGBT%20queer%20students%20in%20the%20SC%20and%20the%20ST%20categories%20will%20struggle%20to%20prove%20that%20the%20discrimination%20against%20them%20is%20on%20grounds%20only%20of%20caste%2C%20because%20it%20could%20well%20be%20because%20of%20their%20gender%20identity%20and%20sexual%20orientation%20%3Cem%3Ealong%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewith%20caste.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECommon%20Situations%20Of%20Discrimination%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDiscrimination%20can%20be%20better%20understood%20in%20the%20context%20of%20its%20commonly%20recurring%20situations.%20In%20addition%20to%20naming%20the%20specificity%20of%20students%20in%20the%20SC%20and%20the%20ST%20categories%2C%20the%20third%20clause%20of%20the%202012%20regulation%20lists%20eight%20situations%20of%20discrimination%20that%20operate%20squarely%20within%20the%20framework%20of%20admissions.%20Other%20sub-clauses%20further%20list%2017%20situations%20that%20operate%20more%20broadly%20%E2%80%9Con%20the%20basis%20of%20caste%2C%20creed%2C%20religion%2C%20language%2C%20ethnicity%2C%20gender%20and%20disability%26quot%3B.%20Doing%20away%20with%20all%20these%20situations%20in%20the%202025%20draft%20regulations%20shows%20that%20the%20contexts%20integral%20to%20applying%20anti-discrimination%20frameworks%20have%20been%20missed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E'Effect%20versus%20intention'%20is%20another%20classic%20matter%20related%20to%20non-discrimination.%20Intent%20is%20famously%20obscure%2C%20because%20it%20occurs%20in%20the%20minds%20of%20perpetrators%2C%20while%20the%20effects%20of%20discrimination%20are%20more%20clearly%20discernible.%20The%20respective%20caste%20compositions%20of%20the%20priestly%20and%20the%20janitorial%20functions%20are%20the%20discernible%20effects%20of%20discrimination.%20Unconscious%20bias%2C%20such%20as%20the%20association%20of%20courage%20and%20strength%20with%20the%20warrior%20caste%20%3Cem%3EKshatriya%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20often%20works%20in%20the%20favour%20of%20students%20from%20this%20caste%20group%20when%20it%20comes%20to%2C%20say%2C%20assigning%20leadership%20roles%20in%20sports%20committees%3B%20they%20may%20be%20preferred%20over%20students%20from%20SC%20and%20ST%20categories%20because%20of%20their%20perceived%20'weakness'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20caste-based%20decisions%20may%20not%20be%20consciously%20intended%2C%20yet%20the%20effects%20are%20discernible%20in%20caste-based%20stereotypes%20reproduced%20in%20contemporary%20scenarios%20on%20campuses.%20Mindful%20of%20this%2C%20the%202012%20regulations%20define%20discrimination%20as%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20purpose%20or%20effect%E2%80%9D.%20The%202025%20draft%20regulations%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20appear%20to%20have%20missed%20this%20significance%20of%20%3Cem%3Eeffect%20%3C%2Fem%3Ealtogether.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EImplement%2C%20Don't%20Overhaul%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20narrower%20definition%20of%20the%202025%20draft%20could%20be%20understood%20in%20a%20longer%20trajectory%20of%20anti-caste%20legislation%20in%20India.%20The%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%20the%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(Prevention%20of%20Atrocities)%20Act%2C%201989%2C%20Section%203%20conceives%20of%20only%20persons%20in%20the%20SC%20and%20the%20ST%20categories%20as%20protected%20groups.%20The%20Protection%20of%20Civil%20Rights%20Act%20of%201955%20defined%20civil%20rights%20as%20%E2%80%9Caccruing%20to%20a%20person%20by%20reason%20of%20the%20abolition%20of%20%E2%80%98untouchability'%20by%20Article%2017%20of%20the%20Constitution%E2%80%9D.%20This%20caste%20particularity%20of%20the%20law%20is%20not%20ideal%2C%20but%20it%20can%20be%20justified%20in%20the%20light%20of%20disproportionately%20higher%20violence%20and%20discrimination%20against%20persons%20from%20the%20SC%20and%20the%20ST%20categories.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20non-intersectional%20approach%20and%20the%20dispensing%20of%20commonly%20recurring%20situations%20of%20discrimination%20and%20their%20effects%20are%20wholly%20unjustifiable%20in%20the%202025%20draft.%20The%20existing%202012%20regulations%20must%20be%20implemented%20more%20diligently%20rather%20than%20being%20replaced%20with%20something%20less%20effective.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Dr%20Sumit%20Baudh%20is%20a%20professor%20of%20law%20at%20O.P.%20Jindal%20Global%20University.%20Views%20expressed%20here%20are%20personal.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742886480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F6l8is96_students_625x300_25_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fugcs-latest-caste-rules-when-the-cure-worsens-a-disease-8005118%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20UGC%202012%20regulations%20must%20be%20implemented%20more%20diligently%20rather%20than%20being%20replaced%20with%20a%20less%20effective%20draft.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fugcs-latest-caste-rules-when-the-cure-worsens-a-disease-8005118%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BAction%20On%20Me%20Illegal%2C%20This%20Is%20Legal%26quot%3B%3A%20Kangana%20Ranaut%20Amid%20Kunal%20Kamra%20Row%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBJP%20MP%20and%20actor%20Kangana%20Ranaut%20has%20slammed%20Kunal%20Kamra's%20jokes%20targeting%20Shiv%20Sena%20chief%20Eknath%20Shinde%20and%20said%20it%20was%20not%20okay%20to%20disrespect%20someone%20for%20his%20humble%20background.%20The%20actor%2C%20who%20was%20at%20the%20receiving%20end%20of%20bulldozer%20action%20during%20the%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20regime%2C%20has%20said%20the%20move%20against%20her%20was%20%26quot%3Billegal%26quot%3B%2C%20but%20the%20action%20being%20taken%20against%20the%20comic%20is%20%26quot%3Blegal%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20MP's%20remarks%20come%20amid%20a%20massive%20row%20over%20Shiv%20Sena%20workers%20vandalising%20a%20Mumbai%20studio%20to%20protest%20Kunal%20Kamra's%20parody%20targeting%20Mr%20Shinde%2C%20now%20the%20Maharashtra%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister.%20The%20vandalism%20has%20been%20followed%20by%20a%20demolition%20exercise%20at%20the%20Khar%20studio%2C%20with%20civic%20officials%20citing%20building%20law%20violations.%20The%20timing%20of%20the%20civic%20action%20has%20raised%20questions%2C%20stoking%20a%20debate%20on%20freedom%20of%20speech%20and%20its%20limits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20the%20media%20outside%20Parliament%2C%20Ms%20Ranaut%20said%20she%20does%20not%20want%20to%20connect%20what%20happened%20to%20her%20with%20what's%20happening%20now.%20%26quot%3BThat%20was%20illegal%2C%20this%20is%20illegal.%20You%20can%20be%20anyone%2C%20but%20insulting%20someone%20is%20(wrong).%20A%20man%20for%20whom%20respect%20is%20everything%2C%20you%20are%20insulting%20him%20in%20the%20name%20of%20comedy.%20You%20are%20disregarding%20his%20work.%20Shindeji%20used%20to%20ply%20an%20auto-rikshaw%20at%20some%20point.%20Now%20he%20has%20risen%20so%20much%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESlamming%20Kamra%2C%20the%20actor%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20are%20his%20credentials%3F%20Who%20are%20these%20people%20who%20could%20not%20achieve%20anything%20in%20life%3F%20Abusing%20in%20the%20name%20of%20comedy%2C%20mocking%20our%20religious%20texts%20and%20joking%20about%20our%20mothers%20and%20sisters.%20They%20call%20themselves%20influencers%20and%20do%20this%20for%20two%20minutes%20of%20fame.%20Where%20is%20our%20society%20headed%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20Maharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20has%20rightly%20said%20that%20people%20need%20to%20take%20responsibility%20for%20their%20actions%20and%20speech.%20%26quot%3BSo%2C%20do%20not%20link%20that%20episode%20with%20this.%20That%20was%20illegal%2C%20this%20action%20is%20legal%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKangana%20Ranaut%20vs%20Shiv%20Sena%20In%202020%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20September%202020%2C%20a%20part%20of%20Kangana%20Ranaut's%20office%20in%20Mumbai's%20Pali%20Hill%20was%20demolished%20by%20the%20Brihanmumbai%20Municipal%20Corporation%20on%20the%20grounds%20of%20encroachment.%20The%20timing%20of%20the%20civic%20action%2C%20however%2C%20raised%20questions.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20the%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20government%20was%20in%20power%20in%20Maharashtra%20and%20also%20controlled%20the%20Mumbai%20civic%20body.%20The%20action%20against%20Kangana%20followed%20a%20bitter%20spat%20between%20her%20and%20Shiv%20Sena%20leaders%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20actor%20Sushant%20Singh%20Rajput's%20shocking%20death.%20She%20also%20compared%20Mumbai%20to%20Pakistan-Occupied%20Kashmir%2C%20alleging%20poor%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20in%20the%20city.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20she%20was%20not%20a%20BJP%20member%20and%20the%20Sena%20had%20not%20been%20split.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20actor%20had%20moved%20the%20court%20against%20the%20demolition%20and%20scored%20a%20big%20win%20there.%20The%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20had%20paused%20the%20demolition%20exercise%20and%20questioned%20the%20motives%20behind%20the%20BMC's%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20massive%20row%20surrounding%20the%20cases%20and%20police%20action%20against%20Kunal%20Kamra%2C%20and%20the%20Opposition's%20support%20for%20the%20comic%2C%20a%20section%20has%20cited%20Kangana%20Ranaut's%20example.%20They%20have%20also%20called%20out%20the%20Uddhav%20Thackeray-led%20party%20on%20its%20support%20for%20Kunal%20Kamra%20and%20accused%20it%20of%20hypocrisy.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742886420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fiuiluhgg_kangana-kamra-_625x300_25_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkunal-kamra-eknath-shinde-kangana-ranaut-action-on-me-illegal-this-is-legal-kangana-ranaut-amid-kunal-kamra-row-8005245%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22BJP%20MP%20and%20actor%20Kangana%20Ranaut%20has%20slammed%20Kunal%20Kamra's%20jokes%20targeting%20Shiv%20Sena%20chief%20Eknath%20Shinde%20and