sport%20are%20encouraged%20to%20deliver%20meals%20directly%20to%20the%20unit.%20If%20not%2C%20the%20team%20arranges%20pick-ups%20through%20Swiggy%20Genie%20or%20Porter.%20Amit%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20operations%20team%20manages%20everything%20from%20pick-up%20to%20delivery.%20For%20larger%20quantities%2C%20like%20three%20kg%20of%20rajma%2C%20if%20the%20home%20cook%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20suitable%20containers%2C%20we%20provide%20huge%20plastic%20boxes%20for%20them%20to%20fill%20and%20send%20back%20to%20us.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-03-20-at-20.05.47-1_11zon-1742741435-500x667.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Spice%20Up%20foods%20has%20served%20over%2015%2C000%20meals%20across%20India%20and%20internationally%20so%20far%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-03-20-at-20.05.47-1_11zon-1742741435-500x667.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-03-20-at-20.05.47-1_11zon-1742741435-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-03-20-at-20.05.47-1_11zon-1742741435-768x1024.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-03-20-at-20.05.47-1_11zon-1742741435-1152x1536.jpeg%201152w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-03-20-at-20.05.47-1_11zon-1742741435-900x1200.jpeg%20900w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-03-20-at-20.05.47-1_11zon-1742741435-600x800.jpeg%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-03-20-a