g%2C%20and%20healing%20the%20lives%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F368737%2Fpriyatama-sharma-child-sexual-abuse-survivor-education-women-educate-your-girls%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echildren%20affected%20by%20sexual%20abuse%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArpan%2C%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20leading%20organisations%20working%20to%20address%20child%20sexual%20abuse%20(CSA)%2C%20has%20been%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20this%20critical%20issue%20for%20nearly%20two%20decades.%20Founded%20in%202007%20by%20Pooja%20Taparia%2C%20the%20organisation%20has%20developed%20a%20comprehensive%20approach%20to%20prevention%2C%20education%2C%20and%20healing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202003%2C%20Taparia%20had%20a%20moment%20that%20changed%20everything.%20%E2%80%9CI%20watched%20the%20play%20named%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3E30%20Days%20in%20September%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20understood%20the%20lasting%20trauma%20that%20can%20be%20experienced%20by%20adult%20survivors%20of%20childhood%20sexual%20abuse.%20It%20was%20a%20wake-up%20call%20and%20I%20felt%20the%20urge%20to%20do%20something%20through%20my%20organisation%20to%20help.%20I%20wanted%20to%20focus%20on%20education%20and%20prevention%20to%20stop%20this%20abuse%20from%20happening%20in%20the%20first%20place%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201156px)%20100vw%2C%201156px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FIMG-20250301-WA0009-1-1742568966.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221156%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20goal%20of%20Arpan%20NGO%2