%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20nothing%20could%20compete%20with%20Sunday%20lunches%2C%20where%20the%20table%20brimmed%20with%20authentic%20South%20Indian%20dishes.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20a%20feast!%20Sometimes%2C%20friends%20and%20relatives%20would%20drop%20by%2C%20and%20other%20times%2C%20we%20would%20have%20unexpected%20guests%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chef%20Sriram%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20came%20to%20choosing%20a%20career%2C%20Chef%20Sriram%20ventured%20into%20law%2C%20but%20later%2C%20at%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20behest%2C%20he%20explored%20culinary%20pursuits.%20He%20joined%20the%20Institute%20of%20Hotel%20Management%2C%20Catering%20Technology%20and%20Applied%20Nutrition%20in%20India%20in%201984%20and%20followed%20this%20up%20with%20a%20post-graduate%20degree%20in%20food%20production%20skills%20and%20management%20from%20Mumbai%2C%20which%20paved%20his%20way%20into%20the%20Taj%20Hotel%20in%20Mumbai.%20Here%2C%20the%20young%20chef%20was%20exposed%20to%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20best%20chefs%2C%20talent%2C%20and%20the%20finest%20ingredients%E2%80%9D.%20His%20subsequent%20travels%20around%20the%20world%20made%20him%20cognisant%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F357260%2Fbest-street-food-mumbai-chef-sanjyot-keer-your-food-lab-ashok-vada-pav-mamledar-misal-elco-bandra%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epotential%20of%20Indian%20flavours%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20made%20him%20want%20to%20formalise%20his%20love%20affair%20with%20food.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20first%20project%20was%20the%20%E2%80%98Karavalli%E2%80%99%20restaurant%2C%20created%20in%201990%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20which%20went%20on%20to%20be%20featured%20among%20the%20World%E2%80%99s%20Best%20Restaurants.%20Then%20came%20the%20London-based%20%E2%80%98Bombay%20Brasserie%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20he%20started%20in%201982%20%E2%80%94%20the%20venture%20helped%20Parsi%2C%20Gujarati%2C%20and%20Maharashtrian%20fare%20find%20their%20footing%20among%20epicurean%20choices%20%E2%80%94%20followed%20by%20Quilon%20in%201999.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ERetaining%20the%20glint%20of%20the%20MICHELIN%20Star%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChef%20Sriram%E2%80%99s%20tables%20have%20seen%20the%20likes%20of%20former%20prime%20ministers%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20and%20Dr%20Manmohan%20Singh%2C%20Sir%20John%20Major%2C%20Prince%20Charles%2C%20Roger%20Federer%2C%20AR%20Rahman%2C%20Sunil%20Gavaskar%2C%20Tom%20Cruise%2C%20and%20Madonna%2C%20among%20other%20national%20and%20international%20celebrities.%20He%20is%20also%20the%20only%20Indian%20chef%20to%20have%20cooked%20at%20the%20World%20Economic%20Forum%20in%20Davos%20continuously%20for%20the%20past%2016%20years.%20He%20says%20he%20owes%20his%20success%20to%20the%20holy%20triad%20%E2%80%94%20the%20right%20technique%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F268194%2Fgujju-ben-na-nasta-mumbai-best-breakfast-inspiring-woman-entrepreneur-grandmother-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eauthentic%20ingredients%2C%20and%20passion%20for%20the%20craft%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2Fquilon-south-indian-food-3-1742212089.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bold%20flavours%20and%20succulent%20meats%20form%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20Quilon%20menu%20in%20London%2C%20winning%20it%20a%20MICHELIN%20Star%20for%2014%20years%20in%20a%20row%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5